<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c5">طالب:</span> هي نجسة يا شيخ؟<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>لا، ما دامت يابسة.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
